QuestData.Title: Botani Beatdown
QuestData.Description: Gidwin is doing much better. Thank you, $n.$b$bI can't believe the draenei have lived alongside those horrible monsters for so long.$b$bMaybe we should show these beasts what happens when you mess with an Azerothian.
QuestData.RewardText: That's what I'm talking about! Great work out there, $n.
